        {
            "id": 6419886,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 雅特力-KY(6907)大漲7.32%，報132元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>雅特力-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6907:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6907\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6907-TW</a>)14日11:20股價上漲9元，報132.0元，漲幅7.32%，成交382張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>雅特力-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6907:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6907\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6907-TW</a>)所屬產業為半導體業，主要業務為各種積體電路之研究、設計開發、製造及銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲25.25%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲10.8%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-96 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-96 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6419886",
